
A really simple ASCII pokemon-themed CTF framework coded during a weekend for some training
with my teammates.

Forked from: https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ascii-ctf

To create the pokemon pngs in ascii art I used the `ansize` tool.To convert ansi color codes to html, I used `aha`.


# Additional Credits

Pokemon sprites from: https://www.kaggle.com/kvpratama/pokemon-images-dataset
Blurry ascii hack from: http://www.briankhuu.com/blog/self/2015/01/14/css-style-for-ascii-art.html
ASCII banner generator: http://www.network-science.de/ascii/
Ansize: https://github.com/jhchen/ansize
Aha: https://github.com/theZiz/aha
